26:58.160 --> 27:00.002
Not in time sequence.

27:00.022 --> 27:00.743
Not in time sequence.

27:00.763 --> 27:00.943
No.

27:01.864 --> 27:03.305
I follow the day by day.

27:03.606 --> 27:05.368
There's no changing there.

