45:03.068 --> 45:09.216
but other kinds of growths you see, which really makes the literature interesting.

45:09.316 --> 45:12.019
Do you see a forest growing?

45:12.259 --> 45:19.629
I see a forest drawing, yes, with great trees and lesser trees and charming shrubs.

45:24.695 --> 45:28.660
